name: Probar Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Bar (Meal)
description: The flavour combination from your favourite cookies, in a bar that delivers real nourishment.Ingredients: brown rice syrup, oats, chocolate chips (dried cane syrup, chocolate liquor, cocoa butter), peanut butter (peanuts), roasted peanut pieces, sunflower seeds, dates, flax seeds, sesame seeds, almonds, dried cane syrup, crisp brown rice, expeller pressed canola oil, vegetable glycerin, dried pineapple, dried cane syrup, dried papaya, roasted pea extract, citric acid, salt, oat flour, pumpkin seeds, molasses, Arabic gum, natural tocopherols and ascorbic acid (added to present flavour), rosemary extract.Allergens, contains: almonds, peanuts, oats, sesame.
